name: Bean Coin
description: BEAN is a community-driven meme token on the Ethereum blockchain, inspired by a uniquely memorable and charismatic coffee bean character full of bold, action-packed spirit. It offers fans a decentralized way to celebrate this dynamic character, designed to make a lasting impact on internet culture with its slogan, "Get Beaned." The token features a renounced contract for permanent security, burned liquidity for enhanced stability, and a deflationary supply that decreases with every transaction. Bean Coin is crafted for collectors, enthusiasts, and vibrant community engagement.
